@startuml 07-embed-player

!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
title Flow 7: Video Embedding

actor "Website\nVisitor" as Visitor
participant "Third-party\nWebsite" as Website
participant "Platform\nBackend" as Backend
participant "Platform\nPlayer" as Player

== iframe Embed ==

Visitor -> Website: Visit page with embedded video

Website -> Website: Render HTML:\n<iframe src="https://api.platform.com\n/embed/{video_id}"></iframe>

Website -> Backend: GET /embed/{video_id}

Backend -> Backend: Validate video exists\nCheck bandwidth quota

alt Video available
    Backend --> Website: HTML page with:\n- Video.js / HLS.js player\n- Configured for /v/{video_id}/stream.m3u8\n- Platform branding (optional)

    Website --> Visitor: Render iframe

    Visitor -> Player: Click play
    Player -> Backend: GET /v/{video_id}/stream.m3u8
    note right of Player: Standard HLS flow\n(see Flow 3)

else Video unavailable
    Backend --> Website: Error page:\n"Video unavailable"
    Website --> Visitor: Error displayed
end

== Direct HLS URL (Alternative) ==

note over Website
  Alternative: Direct <video> tag

  <video controls>
    <source src="https://api.platform.com
      /v/{video_id}/stream.m3u8"
      type="application/x-mpegURL">
  </video>

  Requires HLS.js for non-Safari browsers
end note

@enduml
